$Id: NEWS,v 1.14 2003/02/17 19:16:28 telka Exp $

ioperm-0.4 (2003-02-17):

	* Implemented iopl() call with parameter 3. It grants access for whole
		ports range.
	* Minor bugs fixed.

ioperm-0.3 (2003-01-28):

	* Fixed cygioperm-0.dll creation.
	* Dependency on Windows DDK completely removed.
	* Added initial iopl() implementation.
	* Prepared for integration with mainstream Cygwin net distribution.
	* Improved look and feel for ioperm admin tool.
	* Added test for ioperm() return value in spkrtest (fixed crash).

ioperm-0.2.1 (2003-01-20):

	* Windows DDK is optional for compilation now
	* --prefix=/usr parameter for ./configure script is not mandatory now

ioperm-0.2 (2002-09-02):

	* ported to Windows 95/98/Me

ioperm-0.1 (2002-07-17):

	* first public release
